The Secretary may cancel at any time the registration of any youth organisation if he is satisfied that it is expedient so to do on the ground that—
(a) the terms of the Constitution or rules of such organisation are, in his opinion, in any respect repugnant to or inconsistent with the provisions of any law for the time being in force in Zambia;
